<?xml version="1.0" encoding="utf-8"?>
<Subtitle>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>1</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>11088</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>15485</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>悟空落到另一座山的山顶上。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>2</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>15491</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>21048</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“啊嚏！”悟空呻吟道，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>3</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>21050</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>27882</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“那火和烟太可怕了！还有沙，全都……</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>4</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>27882</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>32595</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>啊……啊……啊嚏……进我鼻子里去了。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>5</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>32596</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>35672</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他看了看赛太岁的山。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>6</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>35673</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>38889</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>现在，火和烟都消失了。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>7</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>38890</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>42684</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>悟空正要回到那座山去，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>8</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>42685</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>46344</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>但是他开始犹豫起来。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>9</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>46345</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>50524</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“妖怪还会使用相同的法术的。”悟空想，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>10</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>50525</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>52785</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我得偷偷到他的洞里去看看。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>11</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>52786</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>57560</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>也许能搞清楚他是怎么制造出火、烟和沙的。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>12</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>57561</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>64739</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>悟空变成虫子，又飞到妖怪的山上。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>13</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>64740</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>73379</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他飞进洞里，经过一条又长又黑的隧道。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>14</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>73380</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>77797</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>很快，他发现一个亮着灯的房间。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>15</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>77798</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>82826</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>那里放满了漂亮的家具，装饰很华丽。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>16</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>82827</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>90632</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>在角落里，一个女人正坐在椅子上哭泣。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>17</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>90654</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>95178</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>噗！悟空变回自己的样子。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>18</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>95179</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>97885</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“哦！”那个女人大喊，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>19</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>97885</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>100135</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“你，你是谁？”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>20</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>100135</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>103385</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我叫孙悟空。”悟空说，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>21</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>103393</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>105301</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“您是王后吗？”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>22</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>105302</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>108229</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>那个女人点了点头。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>23</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>108230</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>111598</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“您丈夫叫我来救您。”悟空说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>24</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>111600</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>116109</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>王后的脸上忽然出现了笑容。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>25</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>116119</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>118753</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“哦，求你一定救救我！</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>26</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>118754</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>120726</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>这个妖怪太可怕了。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>27</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>120623</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>125598</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他又坏又丑又臭！”王后颤抖了一下。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>28</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>125599</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>129780</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“他说他爱我，想……想和我结婚！”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>29</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>129781</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>132898</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>王后又开始哭起来。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>30</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>132899</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>136219</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“您别担心，王后。”悟空说，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>31</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>136220</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>138470</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我会打败那个妖怪的。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>32</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>138471</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>143308</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>可是，我得先知道他是怎么制造出火、烟和沙的。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>33</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>143308</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>147149</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“那很简单。”王后抽了一下鼻子，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>34</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>147150</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>149313</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“他有三个铃铛。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>35</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>149314</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>151541</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>第一个铃铛造火，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>36</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>151542</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>154081</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>第二个铃铛造烟，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>37</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>154082</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>156694</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>第三个铃铛造沙。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>38</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>156697</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>160672</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我也看到那几个铃铛了。”悟空说，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>39</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>160673</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>164636</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“他把铃铛挂在了脖子上。”悟空笑了。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>40</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>164637</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>166665</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“您在这儿等着，王后。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>41</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>166666</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>169381</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>今晚，我要偷来妖怪的铃铛。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>42</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>169382</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>173288</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>等我打败了那个妖怪，再回来救您。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>43</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>173289</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>179450</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>悟空重新变成虫子，又飞进另一个隧道。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>44</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>179451</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>185602</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>很快，他就找到了第二个房间。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>45</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>185603</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>189176</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>这个房间又黑又暗。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>46</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>189177</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>192231</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“这一定是妖怪的。”悟空想，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>47</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>192232</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>196249</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我得在这儿等着，直到妖怪睡着。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>48</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>196249</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>200449</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他落到天棚上等着。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>49</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>200450</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>205605</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>不一会儿，赛太岁走进房间来。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>50</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>205613</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>210142</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>悟空看见了妖怪脖子上挂着的铃铛。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>51</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>210143</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>218968</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“今天真的好忙啊。”妖怪说，“好累啊。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>52</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>218977</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>223270</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>妖怪上床，闭上了眼睛。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>53</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>223276</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>227531</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>很快，就大声地打起了呼噜。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>54</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>227532</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>230773</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>悟空又变回自己的样子。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>55</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>230774</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>236084</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他拔下几根毛变成了跳蚤。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>56</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>236008</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>242071</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>那些跳蚤落到妖怪的脖子上开始咬他。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>57</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>242072</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>245673</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>妖怪挠了挠脖子，翻了个身。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>58</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>245674</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>248137</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>然后，他又挠了挠。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>59</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>248138</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>250450</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>然后，又挠了挠。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>60</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>250451</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>253354</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>最后，妖怪坐了起来。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>61</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>253351</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>256995</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“怎么脖子这么痒呢？”他说，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>62</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>256996</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>260384</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“可能是因为这几个铃铛。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>63</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>260385</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>263283</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>睡觉时，我得把它们摘下来。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>64</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>263284</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>267403</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>妖怪把三个铃铛放到了桌子上。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>65</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>267279</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>271073</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>几分钟后，他又开始打呼噜。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>66</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>271074</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>275934</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>跳蚤重新变成毛，回到了悟空手里。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>67</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>275937</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>282409</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>然后，悟空把那些毛变成了三个假铃铛。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>68</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>282410</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>286171</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他把那几个铃铛放到桌子上，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>69</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>286172</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>289477</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>把真铃铛放进了上衣里。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>70</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>289478</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>292757</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他看了看正在睡觉的妖怪。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>71</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>292758</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>297276</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“在这里用这些铃铛太危险了。”悟空想，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>72</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>297277</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>301109</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“得把妖怪引到外面后，再跟他打。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>73</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>301976</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>307575</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>悟空隐身，沿着隧道跑了出来。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>74</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>307576</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>311793</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>一个小妖在洞口睡觉。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>75</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>312117</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>316495</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>悟空悄悄走过了他。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>76</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>316496</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>324544</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>悟空一到外面，就大喊道：“马上放了王后！</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>77</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>324545</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>330728</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>不然，我就毁了你的山！”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
</Subtitle>